du renforcement.

00:05:53.780 --> 00:05:55.680
Qui est ce type ?

00:05:56.590 --> 00:05:57.930
Ne me dis pas que…

00:05:59.570 --> 00:06:01.250
tu y as mis
toutes tes forces ?

00:06:09.290 --> 00:06:12.000
Tu as un humour
particulier.

00:06:12.310 --> 00:06:13.700
