passons à 50 % !

00:06:38.790 --> 00:06:39.960
Enfoiré !

00:06:51.770 --> 00:06:52.710
Merde !

00:06:53.020 --> 00:06:55.500
Tu ne te déplaces
pas trop mal,

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:56.300
